    "YangsThoughts": "The Crusader RV remains about as iconic as a Warhammer in the Heavy class of 'Mechs.  House Liao looked around at the changing landscape of war and decided to make some subtle increases to the close range firepower should it run into an enemy 'Mech up close. That said they also removed the Jump Jets so it couldnt get away if that encounter went awry. All things considered, the amount of increased armor on this variant is truly obscene.", 
